                        <p xml:id="auto_1mohghxy">
                            <b>Equal Speeds:</b> Set both Car A and Car B to the exact same speed (e.g., 10 m/s). Start the animation. What happens to the "Relative Speed" readout? Does the distance gap between them ever change?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li xml:id="auto_08rww5by">
                        <p xml:id="auto_n5i2v7c8">
                            <b>The Overtake:</b> Set Car A (the rear car) to a higher speed than Car B. Observe the "Distance Covered" labels. Even though Car A starts behind, why does its "Distance Covered" increase faster than Car B's?
                        </p>
